snippet.textDisplay:
That's an absolute poetic masterpiece...🤌🏻✨
I used to listen to this song on Spotify so never got to see the music video. My conception about the story was different. I thought two people who once loved each other got separated due to some misunderstandings or something in the past and they might have met at some party coincidentally in the present and the lirycs are their pov's for each other and
Finally they get united.

Saw the music vdo on my friend's recommendation today and the real story is pretty different and more painful from what I thought.
 
Though I'd still like to be in my delulu as it has a happy ending 😄

This is the kind of content, quality ecpected from coke studio. I personally loved the music as its soo catchy that once you listen it runs in your mind throughout the day🤌🏻
